      <title>意大利预算因 Meloni 下调 2023 年债务而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利数据经过多年修订后，其债务比率降低了近三个百分点，这为意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府在准备公布新的预算目标时提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者消化新内阁 法债市场风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶（Michel Barnier）新内阁所面临的挑战及其控制国家巨额赤字的能力，法国政府债券表现落后于其他债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坦桑尼亚在抗议活动前逮捕反对派领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/tanzania-arrests-opposition-leaders-ahead-of-planned-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坦桑尼亚警方逮捕了主要反对党领导人，原因是他们要求支持者参加被禁的街头抗议活动，要求停止政治绑架和谋杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/tanzania-arrests-opposition-leaders-ahead-of-planned-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强对黎巴嫩真主党的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列周一早上加强了对黎巴嫩南部真主党的空袭，并敦促平民撤离该地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国央行行长支持巴尼耶的富人税政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/bank-of-france-chief-backs-barnier-s-tax-the-rich-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛全力支持新政府提出的向富人和大公司征税的提议，以紧急缓解紧张的公共财政状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/bank-of-france-chief-backs-barnier-s-tax-the-rich-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基访问美国，首先参观拜登家乡的弹药厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/zelenskiy-starts-us-trip-at-ammunition-plant-in-biden-s-hometown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泽连斯基首次访美之旅首先参观了宾夕法尼亚州的一家弹药厂，宾夕法尼亚州是一个关键的摇摆州，将决定11月美国总统大选的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/zelenskiy-starts-us-trip-at-ammunition-plant-in-biden-s-hometown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 05:29:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯誓言英国预算紧张前不会重回紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 周一承诺，英国新工党政府不会恢复保守党前任政府的紧缩政策。在连续数周警告公共财政状况严峻之后，她将转向更为积极的论述。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理考虑对富裕和大型企业征税以解决债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了弥补法国庞大的预算赤字并安抚国际投资者，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 决定对富人和大公司征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼总统就任，国际货币基金组织担忧加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡新任左翼总统于周一宣誓就职，他赶走了该国精英阶层，选民指责这些精英导致国家破产，并实施与国际货币基金组织救助计划相关的严厉紧缩措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非团结党在市场乐观情绪中迎来成立 100 天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西里尔·拉马福萨重新掌权并领导的非洲人国民大会同意与反对党组成执政联盟已经 100 天了。尽管联盟被认为提振了市场情绪，但可以说，拉马福萨之前的改革才是当前乐观情绪的推动者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 11:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
